originalText.text: Was charged twice for nutra caps on 12-14 never received the product. Called and talked to Ben was put on eternal hold, needless to say hung up after over 20 minutes. Called back  Supervisor  Tiffany was to have Manager Kay call back.  An hour later no call from Kay so here we are calling back. Eric is the first one to really be helpful!  This is not the first problem!  After 15 yrs may have to go elsewhere.

originalText.text: This would have gotten one star,  but they wound up giving me the order for free after I had cancelled my check. Horrible customer service with no follow up.  It took over a month to get my order after I sent a check via priority mail which they received 2 days later. Save yourself the hassle and order from amazon, ebay, etc. I didn't order from them online because their site was setting off security alerts on my computer. Shady all around.
